<br>
Dont know.. Ask Itz.. I am sure he knows all the &quot;secrets&quot;<br>
<br>
2. Did she make the same deal with you that was made the previous 2 times CT was up for her raids?<br>
<br>
See #1<br>
<br>
3. The previous 2 times that Conquest got CT, Conquest was at the Fear portal and ready to go up BEFORE Cicely/Amalaya was ready to take her raid up. Was this also the case on the day of the IF/TSO incident?<br>
<br>
Factually, Conquest started porting over to the Ferrot right about the time we pulled the temple.<br>
<br>
4. Did Cicely/Amalaya and Deavi have enough people IN FEAR to take out CT before Conquest was ready at the Fear Portal?<br>
<br>
More than enough, in fact on either this thread or another, Conquest was complaining about us taking 100 people to kill CT.<br>
<br>
5. As was stated about the previous 2 CT slayings by Conquest, Amalaya/Cicely had a time limit placed on her to get in and clear the plane. Could her calling in additional help to clear the plane possible be so she could actually get to and take down the majority of the plane before Conquest came up to take CT?<br>
<br>
The time limit was placed by Frizz, before we pulled the temple. We had 2.5 hours to kill CT (which was only enough for one attempt if we had had the temple pulled, maybe 2). We hadnt gone over the instructions for CT at that point yet because we still had to pull the temple.<br>
<br>
6. It was mentioned that Cicely/Deavi thought they 'had one chance at this.' Was an agreement made that had Cicely/Amalaya's raid failed to take down CT on the first go-round, Conquest would get their shot at him?<br>
<br>
As mentioned we had a 2.5 hour window to take him. Which, with the temple NOT pulled was enough for one hard attempt, maybe 2 if we pushed it.<br>
<br>
<br>
<br>
